<plot>Naked Planet showcases nature's finest icons in a style never seen before. The Academy Award winning aerial system ; Flying Cam ; takes the viewer over the lip of Niagara Falls before free-falling into the dizzy gorge below; endoscope, periscope and ultra-wide angle lenses capture views of the earth through animals' eyes; and 3D computer animation brings alive the geology which led to the creation of each masterpiece.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?388738</url></doc>
